<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No. I would say the same thing about Chaim Potok&apos;s other books, which I have read for many years. You will learn a lot about the Jewish faith and cult<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">â€¦more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No. I would say the same thing about Chaim Potok's other books, which I have read for many years. You will learn a lot about the Jewish faith and culture from his books, but I was raised Christian and it certainly not a requirement to be of the Jewish faith to appreciate his beautiful stores and writing.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
