<div id="review_2710130994" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2710130994" />
    <a title="Laine" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10067611-laine"><img alt="Laine" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1339115987p2/10067611.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2710130994?book_show_action=true">Feb 19, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Laine" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Laine" href="/user/show/10067611-laine">Laine</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2710130994" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5566733326931947473">What a beautifully written story. Normally I wouldnâ€™t have time for girls coming of age tales written by men but this has a sensitivity that makes it bearable. It takes place in a community and a time that is fraught with conflict. All beliefs are challenged and ultimately proven flawed. Who can argue with that? </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

