          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/12714772-davita-s-harp">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3830946-sue?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3830946-sue?shelf=usa">usa</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3830946-sue?shelf=wwii">wwii</a>, 
